The '''Clone Warriors''' were elite shock troops developed by [[Atha Prime/Legends|Atha Prime]]. They were used against the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] after Prime was freed from his exile by the [[Death/Legends|death]] of [[Galactic Emperor/Legends|Emperor]] [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]]. They were known to have decimated several Rebel outposts and were deployed from Prime's personal [[Starship/Legends|starship]], the [[Annihilator (starship)|''Annihilator'']].<ref name="Tales">{{GalaxyCite|2|Galactic Bazaar|Galactic Bazaar: Tales of Phantom Toys}}></ref>

